source.expression:
let
    Source = DateTime.LocalNow(),
    #"Converted To Table" = #table(1, {{Source}}),
    #"Renamed Column" = Table.RenameColumns(#"Converted To Table", {{"Column1", "Last refresh datetime"}}),
    #"Changed Type" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#"Renamed Column", {{"Last refresh datetime", type datetime}})
in
    #"Changed Type"

VAR startDate =
    MIN ( 'Audit'[Creation time] )
VAR lastRefreshDate =
    MAX ( 'Audit'[Creation time] )
RETURN
    ADDCOLUMNS (
        CALENDAR (
            startDate,
            lastRefreshDate
        ),
        "Date (no year)", [Date],
        "Day", DAY ( [Date] ),
        "Year", YEAR ( [Date] ),
        "Quarter",
            CONCATENATE (
                "Q",
                QUARTER ( [Date] )
            ),
        "Week number",
            WEEKNUM (
                [Date],
                1
            ),
        "Year month",
            YEAR ( [Date] ) & "-"
                & MONTH ( [Date] ),
        "Month number", MONTH ( [Date] ),
        "Month name",
            FORMAT (
                [Date],
                "MMMM"
            ),
        "Day of year",
            DATEDIFF (
                DATE ( YEAR ( [Date] ), 1, 1 ),
                [Date],
                DAY
            ) + 1,
        "Day of week",
            WEEKDAY (
                [Date],
                1
            ),
        "Day name",
            FORMAT (
                [Date],
                "DDD"
            )
    )

let
    Source = Table.FromRows(Json.Document(Binary.Decompress(Binary.FromText("", BinaryEncoding.Base64), Compression.Deflate)), let _t = ((type nullable text) meta [Serialized.Text = true]) in type table [Version = _t, #"Change type" = _t, Page = _t, Comment = _t, Release = _t]),
    #"Changed Data Types" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(Source, {{"Change type", type text}, {"Page", type text}, {"Comment", type text}, {"Release", type text}})
in
    #"Changed Data Types"

measures.name: Active capacities
measures.expression:
CALCULATE(
    DISTINCTCOUNT(Audit[CapacityKeyIndex]), FILTER(Capacity,
        Capacity[Capacity SKU] <> "PPU" &&
        Capacity[Capacity SKU] <> "Pro" &&
        Capacity[CapacityKeyIndex] <> BLANK() &&
        Capacity[CapacityKeyIndex] <> 0
        )
    ) + 0

measures.name: Active users
measures.expression:
CALCULATE(
        DISTINCTCOUNT ( Audit[UserKeyIndex] ) ,
        User[UserKeyIndex] <> BLANK() &&
        User[UserKeyIndex] <> 0
         ) + 0

measures.name: Items
measures.expression: CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('Fabric Items'[Item Id]), USERELATIONSHIP(Workspace[Workspace Id],'Fabric Items'[Workspace Id]),USERELATIONSHIP(Capacity[CapacityKeyIndex],Workspace[CapacityKeyIndex]))

measures.expression: CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('Fabric Items'[Item Id]), USERELATIONSHIP(Workspace[Workspace Id],'Fabric Items'[Workspace Id]),USERELATIONSHIP(Capacity[CapacityKeyIndex],Workspace[CapacityKeyIndex])) + 0

columns.name: Access count bins
columns.expression:
VAR TotalAccessCount = 'Fabric Items'[Direct access count] + 'Fabric Items'[Group access count]

VAR BinText = SWITCH(
    TRUE(),
    TotalAccessCount <= 100, "0-100",
    TotalAccessCount > 100 && TotalAccessCount <= 2000, "101-2000",
    TotalAccessCount > 2000 && TotalAccessCount <= 5000, "2001-5000",
    TRUE(), "5000+"
)

RETURN
    BinText

measures.name: Most used label
measures.expression:
VAR _vals = SUMMARIZE (FILTER('Fabric Items', NOT(ISBLANK('Fabric Items'[MIP label Id]))),'Fabric Items'[Label name],"Count", COUNTAX('Fabric Items', 'Fabric Items'[Label name]))  
VAR _measureMax = MAXX (_vals, [Count])  
VAR _result = CALCULATE (MAXX (FILTER (_vals, [Count] = _measureMax), 'Fabric Items'[Label name]))

RETURN _result

measures.name: Label comp
measures.expression:
VAR _NumIcons_Total = 10
VAR _NumIcons_Full = ROUNDDOWN(DIVIDE([No. of labeled items],[No. of items],0)*10,0)
VAR _NumIcons_empty = _NumIcons_Total-_NumIcons_Full

VAR _FullIcon = "⬤"
VAR _EmptyIcon = "○"

VAR _Bar = IF(_NumIcons_Full <10,REPT(_FullIcon,_NumIcons_Full) & REPT(_EmptyIcon,_NumIcons_empty), REPT("🏆",6))
RETURN
    _Bar

VAR _measureMax = MAXX(Filter('Fabric Items', 'Fabric Items'[Endorsement] IN { "None" }), [Access Count],TRUE) 
VAR Most_accessed_item =if(_measureMax>= [Access parameter], "1","0")

RETURN Most_accessed_item

measures.name: Most disticnt wokspace a creator published to
measures.expression:
VAR _vals = SUMMARIZE ('Fabric Items','Fabric Items'[Created by user Id],"Count", DISTINCTCOUNT('Workspace'[Workspace Id]))  
VAR _measureMax = MAXX (_vals, [Count])  
VAR _UserID = CALCULATE (MAXX (FILTER (_vals, [Count] = _measureMax), 'Fabric Items'[Created by user Id]))
VAR _result = CALCULATE (MAXX (FILTER (User, [User Id] = _UserID), 'User'[User name]))

RETURN _result

measures.name: Most populated WS without domain
measures.expression:
VAR _vals = SUMMARIZE (FILTER('Workspace','Workspace'[DomainKeyIndex] = BLANK() ),'Workspace'[Workspace Id],"Count", [No. of items]) 
VAR _measureMax = MAXX (_vals, [Count])  
VAR _WSID = CALCULATE (MAXX (FILTER (_vals, [Count] = _measureMax), 'Workspace'[Workspace Id]))
VAR _result = CALCULATE (MAXX (FILTER (Workspace, [Workspace Id] = _WSID), 'Workspace'[Workspace name]))

RETURN _result

measures.name: Most Items a creator published outside of a domains count
measures.expression:
VAR _MAX_items = CALCULATE(
                        MAXX(
                            SUMMARIZE('Fabric Items','Fabric Items'[Created by user Id], "Count", [No. of items]), [Count] ),
                            FILTER('Workspace',Workspace[DomainKeyIndex] = BLANK())
)

RETURN _MAX_items

measures.name: Most Items a creator published outside of a domains
measures.expression:
VAR _MAX_items = CALCULATE(
                        MAXX(
                            SUMMARIZE('Fabric Items','Fabric Items'[Created by user Id], "Count", [No. of items]), [Count] ),
                            FILTER('Workspace',Workspace[DomainKeyIndex] = BLANK())
)
VAR _Creator_ID = CALCULATE(
                        MAXX(
                            FILTER (SUMMARIZE('Fabric Items','Fabric Items'[Created by user Id], "Count", [No. of items]), [Count] = _MAX_items), 'Fabric Items'[Created by user Id]),
                            FILTER('Workspace',Workspace[DomainKeyIndex] = BLANK())
                            )


VAR _result = CALCULATE (MAXX (FILTER (User, [User Id] = _Creator_ID), 'User'[User name]))


RETURN _result

measures.name: No. of unendorsed items with view access above threshold
measures.expression:
VAR _Result = CALCULATE(
                        DISTINCTCOUNT(
                            'Fabric Items'[Item Id])+0,
                            FILTER('Fabric Items','Fabric Items'[Endorsement] IN {"None"}),
                            FILTER('Fabric Items',[Access Count] >= 'Access limit to promote endorsement'[Access parameter])
)

RETURN _Result

columns.name: Day Ordinals
columns.expression:
Var Last2Digits = RIGHT('Calendar'[Day of Month],2)
Var LastDigit = RIGHT('Calendar'[Day of Month],1)
Var Ordination =
    SWITCH(TRUE(),
        Last2Digits IN {"11","12","13"},"th",
        LastDigit = "1" , "st",
        LastDigit  = "2","nd",
        LastDigit = "3", "rd",
        "th"
    )
RETURN
CONCATENATE('Calendar'[Day of Month],Ordination)

columns.name: Day Ordinals
columns.expression:
Var Last2Digits = RIGHT('Calendar'[Day of Month],2)
Var LastDigit = RIGHT('Calendar'[Day of Month],1)
Var Ordination =
    SWITCH(TRUE(),
        Last2Digits IN {"11","12","13"},"th",
        LastDigit = "1" , "st",
        LastDigit  = "2","nd",
        LastDigit = "3", "rd",
        "th"
    )
RETURN
CONCATENATE('Calendar'[Day of Month],Ordination)
